# line-string-backslash-literal

## Input

```
a hello\nworld
b path\\to

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..26
  ENTRY@0..15
    WORD_KEY@0..1
      WORD@0..1 "a"
    SPACE@1..2 " "
    LINE_STRING@2..14
      STRING@2..14 "hello\\nworld"
    NEWLINE@14..15 "\n"
  ENTRY@15..26
    WORD_KEY@15..16
      WORD@15..16 "b"
    SPACE@16..17 " "
    LINE_STRING@17..25
      STRING@17..25 "path\\\\to"
    NEWLINE@25..26 "\n"
```

## AST

```
SourceFile {
    shebang: none,
    items: [
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@0..1 "a",
            },
            value: LineString {
                string: STRING@2..14 "hello\\nworld",
            },
        },
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@15..16 "b",
            },
            value: LineString {
                string: STRING@17..25 "path\\\\to",
            },
        },
    ],
}
```

